"This is the first version of the Binary Population Synthesizer (BiPoS1). It allows to efficiently calculate binary distribution functions after the dynamical processing of a realistic population of binary stars..."

"BiPoS1 is compiled by typing \"make BiPoS\" into the command line of a terminal at the directory where the user has stored the program. BiPoS1 should start afterwards, if \"./BiPoS\" is typed into the command line."
